37634>>>        Boolean bHasRecord
37634>>>        Handle hoDD
37634>>>
37634>>>        Get Server to hoDD
37635>>>        Get GetNavigateData to NavigateData
37636>>>        Get HasRecord of hoDD to bHasRecord
37637>>>
37637>>>        // let's hide all buttons and then Show the ones we want
37637>>>        WebSet pbRender of oEditBtn to False
